data.description: Welcome to this spacious and beautifully maintained single-level home in the charming town of White Salmon. This triple-wide gem boasts a generous 2,551 square feet of living space, offering plenty of room for you to grow and thrive. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting interior with a separate family room and living room, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The vaulted ceilings add an airy, open feel to the home, making it perfect for gatherings and creating lasting memories. This home has been thoughtfully updated with a new roof, new carpet, and a new gas water heater, ensuring comfort and peace of mind for years to come. Step outside onto the brand new deck, or meander to the back yard where you can savor the tranquility of your fully fenced yard. For those with hobbies or in need of extra storage space, the oversized detached two-car garage offers versatility and could easily be transformed into a workshop to pursue your creative passions. Situated in a prime location, this home is conveniently located next to schools, making it an ideal choice for many homeowners. Additionally, the nearby walking path that encircles the loop road is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts, providing opportunities for hiking, biking, and leisurely walks. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to call this meticulously cared-for residence your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort, convenience, and beauty this home has to offer. Your dream home in White Salmon awaits allowing you to be in the heart of a vibrant community!
